source: TEXT_CMNBHTREWARDLV020ST0003_00025_TALK_00<tab>Time is of the essence. If you have something to ask, make it quick.
target: TEXT_CMNBHTREWARDLV020ST0003_00025_TALK_00<tab>Nous sommes en pleine mission<var 1D /var>! Ne me dites pas que vous voulez abandonner<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_CMNBHTREWARDLV020ST0003_00025_RETURN_ME_MENU_TITLE<tab>You will be removed from your party. Proceed?

target: TEXT_CMNBHTREWARDLV020ST0003_00025_RETURN_PARTY_MENU_TITLE<tab>L'opération en cours prendra fin. Confirmez-vous votre choix<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNBHTREWARDLV020ST0003_00025_RET_TALK_00<tab>The operation was a success! Here's your reward, and don't let anyone tell you that you didn't earn it.
target: TEXT_CMNBHTREWARDLV020ST0003_00025_RET_TALK_00<tab>Beau travail. Voici une récompense proportionnelle à votre performance.

source: TEXT_CMNBHTREWARDLV020ST0003_00025_RET_SUCCESS_SYSTEM_TALK_00<tab>You will leave the instance once all party members have collected their rewards.
target: TEXT_CMNBHTREWARDLV020ST0003_00025_RET_SUCCESS_SYSTEM_TALK_00<tab>L'opération de guilde est à présent terminée. Vous quitterez l'instance une fois que tous les joueurs auront récupéré leur récompense ou qu'un certain délai se sera écoulé.

source: TEXT_CMNBHTREWARDLV020ST0003_00025_RET_FAIL_TALK_00<tab>Well, well. It looks like you have a full bag.
TEXT_CMNBHTREWARDLV020ST0003_00025_RET_FAIL_SYSTEM_TALK_00<tab>Make room in your inventory and speak with the battlewarden once again to receive your reward.
target: TEXT_CMNBHTREWARDLV020ST0003_00025_RET_FAIL_SYSTEM_TALK_00<tab>Impossible de recevoir la récompense car l'inventaire est plein. Faites de la place et essayez de nouveau.

source: TEXT_CMNBHTREWARDLV020ST0003_00025_AFTER_RWD_TALK_00<tab>Can't you see I'm busy attending to your allies? I don't have time to chat.
target: TEXT_CMNBHTREWARDLV020ST0003_00025_AFTER_RWD_TALK_00<tab>Je distribue les récompenses à vos compagnons. Restez ici un moment.
TEXT_CMNBHTREWARDLV020ST0003_00025_AFTER_RWD_MENU_TITLE<tab>Voulez-vous quitter l'instance sans attendre les autres<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_CMNBHTREWARDLV020ST0003_00025_AFTER_RWD_RETURN_MENU_TITLE<tab>You will be removed from the party. Proceed?

TEXT_CMNBHTREWARDLV020ST0003_00025_FIRST_BONUS_TALK_00<tab>The operation was a success! Here's your payment, and as promised, I've thrown in a little extra, so that you may consider returning to aid us once again.
target: TEXT_CMNBHTREWARDLV020ST0003_00025_FIRST_BONUS_TALK_00<tab>Beau travail. J'ai ajouté un petit quelque chose à votre récompense, pour cette fois.

source: TEXT_CMNBHTREWARDLV020ST0003_00025_FIRST_BONUS_SYSTEM_TALK_00<tab>A bonus has been added to your reward.
target: TEXT_CMNBHTREWARDLV020ST0003_00025_FIRST_BONUS_SYSTEM_TALK_00<tab>Un bonus est attribué lorsqu'une mission est accomplie pour la première fois.
